title: Urlscan.io
description: The OpenCTI URLScan.io connector allows automatic import of phishing URLs from the URLScan.io "Phishing URL Feed", which detects thousands of suspicious, malicious and phishing URLs daily across 680+ tracked brands. The feed of these detected URLs is available to customers to ingest into their Threat Intelligence systems or improve their own security products.
